data.title: 10152 Pheasant Rd #A & B, El Paso, TX 79924
data.meta_description: 10152 Pheasant Rd #A & B, El Paso, TX 79924 is pending. Zillow has 27 photos of this -- beds, -- baths, 2,298 Square Feet multi family home with a list price of $326,000.
data.text: Location is AMAZING! Newly renovated duplex is an investor's dream. The 1-story duplex is great for someone who wants to live on one side and lease or Airbnb the other to reduce their monthly mortgage. A magnificent investment! Each unit is 2BD/1BA with a new refrigerator, appliances, roof, refrigerated a/c, double pane windows, and each with a spacious 1-car garage for a washer, dryer and storage. Each unit has expansive backyards that enhance the property's appeal, offering outdoor space for recreation or potential expansion. The duplex sits on a fantastic location with easy access to Transmountain, I-10, Fort Bliss, schools, restaurants, entertainment, and medical facilities. See this duplex today! Vacant on lockbox.
